info.title: Real Estate Integration Object
info.description: The service contains the Integration Object root as well as several subnodes in order to provide further assignments. Such child objects are for example Object Relations, Contract Assignments, Cost Object Assignments, Conditions, Fixed Asset Assignments and more. All entities support CRUD operations and can therefore be created, read, updated as well as deleted. If there are any issues during processing, the system displays error messages in the response.

x-sap-shortText: Manage Real Estate Integration Objects using this inbound service
